[% IF debug_mode == 1 %]
    [% PageVersion %]
[% END %]

<h1>Schema Management.</h1>

<p>Welcome to the Add Schema page. Here you can manage schema changes for the site.</p>


<form method="post" action="[% c.uri_for('/admin/add_schema') %]">
    <label for="schema_name">Schema Name:</label><br>
    <input type="text" id="schema_name" name="schema_name"><br>
    <label for="schema_description">Schema Description:</label><br>
    <textarea id="schema_description" name="schema_description"></textarea><br>
    <input type="submit" value="Create Migration">
</form>

[% IF error_msg %]
    <p style="color: red;">[% error_msg %]</p>
[% END %]

<p>After creating the migration, you can apply it to the database by clicking the 'Migrate Schema' button.</p>

<form method="post" action="[% c.uri_for('/admin/migrate_schema') %]">
    <input type="submit" value="Migrate Schema">
</form>

<p>For more information or assistance, please contact us.</p>
